SUMMARY:City Chat
DTSTAMP:20260314T153653Z
DTSTART:20260318T160000Z
DESCRIPTION:City Chat presents an excellent opportunity for residents and b
	usiness owners to meet and engage with our new Mayor Stephanie Vignal and 
	Mayor Pro Tem Melissa Duque. Join fellow residents\, ask questions\, and s
	hare their thoughts and opinions. You'll also get updates on City services
	 and learn about upcoming events. This is a great opportunity to share you
	r concerns\, suggestions and more! City Chat is open to the public\, no RS
	VP is required. We hope to see you there!\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/
	events/#/details/city-chat/18254709/2026-03-18T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - All E
	vents
